data.description: Pristine Move in Ready Brick Rancher with newer Windows, newer roof, refinished hardwood floors, newer HVAC. Welcome home to this 3 bedroom 1.5 bath rancher featuring hardwood floors, large eat in kitchen, large living room with wood burning  fireplace, 3 nice size bedrooms, large mudroom which could be used as an office or extra room. Outside features nice size fenced in rear  yard and a carport with side entry to the home. This home is move in ready!!!
